      "span_text": "If moreover H p (A) = 0 for all p > 0, then for objects in D minimal Kprojective resolutions exist (one can either give a direct proof using [K1, Theorem 3.1 c)], or use Proposition 4.9), and the rest of the proof is similar to that of [CITATION_1] Lemma 7.49 ]."
